      <num>SEC. 2.70</num>
      <heading>Created</heading>
      <content>
        <p>To comply with the provisions of Article 5 of
               
               Chapter 1
               
               of Division 1 of the Streets and Highways Code of the State, as amended, there is
               hereby created in the city treasury a special fund to be known as &quot;Special Gas Tax
               Street Improvement Fund.&quot;</p>
        <p>(Code 1938, Sec. 447.)</p>
      </content>
    </section>
